. Professoren publiserer en artikkel om spedbarnsvekt i The Lancet neste uke."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3a332a6b405ef540e0c72d329e9589d57d45988489ecc9c2dc5bcab30b4bcacc"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-23T07:17:27.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- \u00c5 p\u00e5f\u00f8re et foster veksthemning er ingen god id\u00e9, sier psykolog Heidi Furre \u00d8stg\u00e5rder ."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/innenriks/article10053197.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/gravid.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/be3763f4ae8167d6e33c2cfef5ceaf83c269a452.jpg?597d05b3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Gravide sp\u00f8r om slanking flere ganger hver uke -adressa.no", "- Bloggerne har motiv", "Skal legge p\u00e5 seg", "R\u00f8ykeskader", "Gjelder ikke alle", "Ukjent for professor"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "be3763f4ae8167d6e33c2cfef5ceaf83c269a452"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["f\u00f8dt", "f\u00f8dselsvekt", "lav", "lav f\u00f8dselsvekt", "barn", "gravid", "slanke"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["krogh", "the lancet", "oslo universitetssykehus", "aftenposten", "furre \u00f8stg\u00e5rder"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["india", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["siri vond krogh", "ola didrik saugstad", "heidi furre \u00f8stg\u